OL,4,Cchance of survival after fatal ship
OL,5,Cfall
OL,7,FA investigation into the death of an
OL,8,F"experienced" pilot who fell from a
OL,9,Fladder in the Humber Estuary has found
OL,10,Fa number of failings.
OL,12,FThe report by the Marine Accident
OL,13,FInvestigation Branch (MAIB) said there
OL,14,Fwere safety concerns across the
OL,15,F"training, equipment, medical
OL,16,Fstandards and emergency response."
OL,18,FOn 8 January 2023, a pilot fell while
OL,19,Ftrying to board Finnhawk, a cargo
OL,20,Fvessel, after having a cardiac event.
