OL,4,Cchance of survival after fatal ship
OL,5,Cfall
OL,7,FHe hit the deck of the Humber Saturn,
OL,8,Fa pilot vessel, before falling into
OL,9,Fthe water and losing consciousness.
OL,11,FCrew had been unable to raise a
OL,12,Fplatform to recover the pilot -
OL,13,Fleaving him semi-submerged in cold
OL,14,Fwater for over 40 minutes until he
OL,15,Fcould be transferred to a lifeboat.
OL,17,FHe was taken to hospital by a
OL,18,Fcoastguard helicopter where he later
OL,19,Fdied.
