OL,5,Cfall
OL,7,FThe report found the pilot should not
OL,8,Fhave been declared fit to work given
OL,9,Fhe had suffered with several chronic
OL,10,Fhealth conditions, and his "chance of
OL,11,Fsurvival was reduced" by the recovery
OL,12,Fplatform defects.
OL,14,FThe port authority's 'stop work'
OL,15,Fprocedure was unsuccessful in
OL,16,Fpreventing the pilot from working
OL,17,Fdespite "several concerns about his
OL,18,Ffitness being raised by his
OL,19,Fcolleagues," it added.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
