OL,7,FThe Chief Inspector of Marine
OL,8,FAccidents, Andrew Moll OBE, said a
OL,9,Frespected and experienced marine pilot
OL,10,Ftragically lost his life, and urged
OL,11,Fharbour authorities to to learn
OL,12,Flessons from the accident.
OL,14,F"Pilot transfers are challenging and
OL,15,Fpotentially hazardous and fortunately
OL,16,Fmost are conducted without incident.
OL,17,FTragically this was not the case.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
