OL,5,Cfall
OL,7,F"While the MAIB has been encouraged by
OL,8,Fthe actions of the port and industry
OL,9,Fbodies to address these safety issues,
OL,10,FI strongly urge all harbour
OL,11,Fauthorities with a pilotage service to
OL,12,Flearn the lessons of this accident and
OL,13,Ftake action."
OL,15,FThe MAIB recommended the Maritime and
OL,16,FCoastguard Agency to issue guidance
OL,17,Fthat non-SOLAS vessels carry an
OL,18,Falternative means of recovery of an
OL,19,Funconscious person.
