OL,7,FAssociated British Ports has been
OL,8,Frecommended to review its risk
OL,9,Fassessment and update its pilots'
OL,10,Fpersonal protective equipment to
OL,11,Fimprove their survivability in cold
OL,12,Fwater, while port industry bodies have
OL,13,Fbeen asked to issue guidance on the
OL,14,Fsetting of occupational standards for
OL,15,Fmarine pilots and the provision of
OL,16,Fsuitable personal protective equipment
OL,17,Fto improve pilot survivability in cold
OL,18,Fwater.
